Title: Episode Five
Plot: Finn finally tracks down his real father, only to discover that he's close to death. As he tries to build a relationship with him, Finn realises that his newly discovered half-sister might know more about their father's illness than she's letting on. Finn continues his sleuthing in an attempt to win Jess's affection by discovering Alex's hidden secret.
ParentalRatingReason: R18 Violence,offensive language,drug use and sex scenes
